'''加布里埃尔·达·席尔瓦·桑托斯'''（{{lang-pt|Gabriel da Silva Santos}}，{{bd|1996年|5月4日||}}）来自瓜鲁柳斯，是一名巴西男子游泳运动员，主攻自由泳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ecp.org.br/esportes-e-atividades/natacao/equipes/adulto/gabriel-da-silva-santos/|script-title=pt:Gabriel da Silva Santos|work={{lang|pt|Esporte Clube Pinheiros}}|accessdate=2020-07-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222155037/http://www.ecp.org.br/esportes-e-atividades/natacao/equipes/adulto/gabriel-da-silva-santos/|archivedate=2020-02-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

桑托斯曾在2019年7月因为未能通过同年5月进行的一次药检，而被[[国际游泳联合会|国际游泳联合会]]禁赛12个月，他也因此无缘[[2019年世界游泳锦标赛|该年的世界游泳锦标赛]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/gabriel-santos-handed-12-month-ban-after-failing-drugs-test-brazilian-to-miss-tokyo-2020/|title=Gabriel Santos Handed 12-Month Ban After Failing Drugs Test: Brazilian To Miss Tokyo 2020|publisher=Swimming World Magazine|date=2019-07-22|accessdate=2020-07-30|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200730085605/https://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/gabriel-santos-handed-12-month-ban-after-failing-drugs-test-brazilian-to-miss-tokyo-2020/|archivedate=2020-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。桑托斯随后向[[国际体育仲裁法庭|国际体育仲裁法庭]]提出申诉，国际体育仲裁法庭于2020年2月判定其禁赛不成立，宣布解除对他的处罚<ref>{{cite web|url=https://swimswam.com/cas-finds-brazils-gabriel-santos-without-fault-revokes-1-year-suspension|title=CAS Finds Brazil's Gabriel Santos Without Fault, Revokes 1-Year Suspension|work=SwimSwam|date=2020-02-14|accessdate=2020-07-30|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200730090628/https://swimswam.com/cas-finds-brazils-gabriel-santos-without-fault-revokes-1-year-suspension/|archivedate=2020-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

